    <h1>Tag Manager</h1>
    <p class="description">A platform for deploying and managing marketing scripts on your site through a visual interface — <strong>no developer needed for each change</strong>. Google Tag Manager is the dominant tool, used by over 75% of tag-managed websites.</p>
