            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>GTM itself adds a small async script load, but it improves overall page speed by replacing multiple hard-coded scripts with a single managed container. Poorly configured tags that fire synchronously can hurt Core Web Vitals, so always audit tag firing rules.</p></div></div>
          </div>
