            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>GTM maintains a full version history. If a bad publish corrupts data, you can instantly roll back to the previous container version. This is one of the strongest arguments for using a tag manager over hard-coded scripts.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

